Make sure that your version ui-extensions is v0.8.8. You can check by running

```npm view @HubSpot/ui-extensions version```

I doubled check the npm library and PanelBody is exported. You can see  it the <https://www.npmjs.com/package/@HubSpot/ui-extensions?activeTab=code|code tab> on npm.

You can try removing your node_modules folder and your package-lock.json. After that you can re-install everything and try again
